reviews.review_text: Ship of Firecrackers !!! Ah the fond memories of a bunch of M-80's blowing up during Ship of Fools :)

Time Travel What a beautiful audience recording this is. It is like going back in time to when I was there. I have a soundboard copy of this that sounds clear and well balanced but it doesn't capture the feel of the show like this does. You get to hear the notes ring out and the audience responding to their favorite moments.

WOW!%$#@! This is one hell of a show, and the recording is superb.  I just love the audience tapes.  Sitting there with my head phones on, the stereo cranked up - it's the closest thing to a time machine.  Just makes me feel sad for all those who never experienced a live Dead show.
